{"tid":2026601,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"瞞家人上「19禁節目」！　大尺度動作全播出…爸一看暴怒了","createTime":"2020-05-21T05:13:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T06:51:00.000Z","uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"62b566c41fb02eec3029615c83ed3750744e8f57","tid":2026601,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:13:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4890/d4890783.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4890%2Fd4890783.jpg&h=ee82bc40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲南韓女星祚弦。（圖／翻攝IG）<br />\n<br />\n圖文／CTWANT<br />\n<br />\n今年24歲的南韓女星祚弦，是Berry Good成員，最近她上南韓節目《VideoStar》訪談，分享自己的出道故事。他提到，當初自己是瞞著家人偷偷出道，後來爸爸在她出道4個月後，無意間看到自己女兒，竟出現在19禁節目中，穿著露出翹臀的服裝，緊貼男性熱舞，當場氣到差點暈倒。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4890/d4890784.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4890%2Fd4890784.jpg&h=e447b559&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲南韓女星祚弦大跳艷舞，爸爸一度無法接受。（圖／翻攝韓網）<br />\n<br />\n祚弦提到，2016年她出道後，曾到19禁搞笑節目《SNL KOREA第8季》節目當來賓。當時她穿深V緊身上衣，搭配超短熱褲及黑色絲襪，露出爆乳及辣腿的S曲線好身材，在鏡頭前邊搔首弄姿，對著男子跳艷舞，甚至還有幾個舞蹈動作，是以臀部頂對方下體，做出極盡挑逗的誘惑。影片一釋出立刻登上熱搜，祚弦也因此打響知名度。<br />\n<br />\n不過成名代價，就是這個性感指數破表的節目片段，也被爸爸發現了。祚弦表示，爸爸看到影片時，一度無法接受，差點氣到暈倒。還好母親很尊重並支持她的選擇，還幫忙說服父親，勸他讓我做自己想做的事情。後來爸爸經過開導，也慢慢支持女兒的演藝事業，「我現在變得很自豪。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o5QzfDweYj0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Do5QzfDweYj0&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsUzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=e6aa0b78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o5QzfDweYj0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af8258f84560e1a3cfd1d2d423c6a3b92ea08c44","tid":2026601,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:16:44.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"aa423115113fac032191e2f3e2b279bfd0edf6b0","tid":2026601,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"af8258f84560e1a3cfd1d2d423c6a3b92ea08c44","tid":2026601,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:16:44.000Z","msg":"拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:17:32.000Z","msg":"一個CM都冇 咁都拉?"},{"pid":"dc2514441461321c9e3ee2c8963e26d0d6ddf856","tid":2026601,"uid":80162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:18:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39c6271b7d75828227162e399200f6478dd547a5","tid":2026601,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:20:45.000Z","msg":"pull"},{"pid":"2d9e87ab8e281c9d415f10dd999f7a7820472e59","tid":2026601,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39c6271b7d75828227162e399200f6478dd547a5","tid":2026601,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:20:45.000Z","msg":"pull"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:27:14.000Z","msg":"Y"},{"pid":"500f22ef5f972d5997f1401a5d95be9f12462a81","tid":2026601,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:35:02.000Z","msg":"想知點開導爸爸"},{"pid":"fa2f2a37d1c69d516d542b8648c654702bf4b78a","tid":2026601,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"500f22ef5f972d5997f1401a5d95be9f12462a81","tid":2026601,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:35:02.000Z","msg":"想知點開導爸爸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:36:51.000Z","msg":"腿張開"},{"pid":"f691dc3d82c7c394fa6d2d4a9a4d524c81026d29","tid":2026601,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"500f22ef5f972d5997f1401a5d95be9f12462a81","tid":2026601,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor